---
title: 订单处理流程
---
flowchart TD
    classDef startEnd fill:#10B981,stroke:#059669,color:#ffffff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef process fill:#4F46E5,stroke:#3730A3,color:#ffffff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#F59E0B,stroke:#D97706,color:#1E293B,stroke-width:2px
    classDef error fill:#EF4444,stroke:#DC2626,color:#ffffff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef success fill:#06B6D4,stroke:#0891B2,color:#ffffff,stroke-width:2px

    Start([🛒 用户提交订单]):::startEnd

    subgraph 订单验证
        A[接收订单请求]:::process
        B{库存是否充足?}:::decision
        C[锁定库存]:::process
        D[库存不足通知]:::error
    end

    subgraph 支付处理
        E[生成支付订单]:::process
        F{支付是否成功?}:::decision
        G[记录支付信息]:::process
        H[支付失败处理]:::error
        I{重试次数 < 3?}:::decision
    end

    subgraph 订单履约
        J[通知仓库备货]:::process
        K[生成物流单号]:::process
        L[更新订单状态]:::process
        M[发送发货通知]:::success
    end

    Start --> A
    A --> B
    B -->|是| C
    B -->|否| D
    D --> End2([❌ 订单关闭]):::error
    C --> E
    E --> F
    F -->|成功| G
    F -->|失败| H
    H --> I
    I -->|是| E
    I -->|否| End3([⚠️ 人工介入]):::error
    G --> J
    J --> K
    K --> L
    L --> M
    M --> End1([✅ 订单完成]):::startEnd
